# dist is intentionally NOT ignored: local `pnpm build` output is shipped into
# the image instead of rebuilding in Docker, because the cross-platform Docker
# build produces a CSS hash mismatch between the server and client vite passes
# (server bundle hardcodes one styles-*.css hash, client bundle emits another).
# Local builds are deterministic between passes, so we use those. The
# `predeploy` script in package.json ensures dist is fresh before every deploy.
